# Exception: research scripts that drove a production decision and are NOT
# reproducible from the shipped CLI are committed as frozen proofs for the
# findings docs that cite them. They are snapshots, not maintained code:
# excluded from the lint/typecheck/coverage gates (those run on src + tests).
!scripts/learned_scorer_diagnostic.py
!scripts/learned_scorer_tightening.py
!scripts/learned_scorer_decoys.py
!scripts/learned_scorer_heldout.py
!scripts/volume_signal_characterization.py
